data.description: Cute split floor plan 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a wonderful yard and lots of space to make it your own! Vinyl plank flooring throughout living areas, updated kitchen with stainless appliances and a kitchen window view overlooking the peaceful backyard. The living space expands into the enclosed Florida room, under air and perfect for relaxing or working from home. Plenty of natural light and views of the amazing fenced backyard space with lots of room for RV and toys. Additional home features are a screen enclosed back porch, walk-in closet for the primary bedroom, double sinks in the guest bath, great schools, easy access to major highways, beaches, airport and shopping.
